          "type": "info",
          "text": "Status 17/12: Current approach is to design content and master data endpoints for Intel and Enterprise migration target customers (and new Enterprise customers) that represent our desired One API future state, and encourage existng Enterprise customers to them. The original proposal was to make these available on a single subdomain - connect.gocube.global.    There are two parts to this: API end point and contract design.  The starting point was a review of the convergence opportunities between Enterprise and proposed Intel.  Final design of content endpoints is in progress. Technical design to have all sit between connect but be accessible on same or similar domain.  Sid has presented initial proposal.  Needs completion and sign-off."
